  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of Two interdental cleaning devices on plaque removal, gingivitis and bleeding.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study measured plaque accumulation, bleeding on probing and gingivitis using the Rustogi
      Modification of the Navy Plaque Index, BOP and Modified Gingival Index at baseline, 2-weeks
      and 4-weeks.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
